value.0: The fire crackles and burns, consuming everything within its scorching heat. Within the lava-like rock a brazier of magical aura is embedded. It perhaps could be hammered out.

This small golden pan holds smoldering coals. If the coals are stirred up, the brazier will summon a fire elemental to serve the user. It holds enough power to burn at intense heat, enough to perhaps forge even the hardest stone.
This small golden pan appears to hold constantly glowing coals.
High Brazier of Commanding Fire Elementals
